data.title: Girl Names & Meanings
data.meta_description: Get the right name for your daughter from 1000's of girl baby names. This collection of girl names & meanings will help you choose the best name for your baby girl.
data.text: A'dab Hope and need Muslim A'idah Visiting, returning; reward Muslim A'li Exaulted, noble, highest social standing Muslim A'mal One with dreams and aspirations Muslim Aaarti Worship with lamps Hindu Aabidah Worshipper Muslim Aabirah Passer by, Fragrant Muslim Aachal It is name that means steady or immovable Hindu Aadab Hope and need Muslim Aadal Azhagi Hindu Aadarshini It means honour or prestige Hindu Aadharsha It is a hindi word meaning pride, honour Hindu Aadhriti Stalwart Hindu Aadhvitha Unique, one of a kind Hindu Aadhya It means 'first' Hindu Aadila One who is righteous and high in moral Muslim Aadilakshmi It is used to imply Goddess Lakshmi Hindu Aadishree Exalted dignity Hindu Aadrika It means strong, immovable and sturdy Hindu Aadya The Sanskrit girl name Aadya means 'excellent and the first or primeval'.
